eplyTime":"2018-04-11T02:35:58.000Z","msg":"鐘意個啲歌手就點都會買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n純粹當收藏"},{"pid":"f708f27a7c89e3331ac8ff4aa463664d6babe77b","tid":624763,"uid":89866,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T02:39:13.000Z","msg":"我到依家都仲有買嘅<br />\n見到啲好聽嘅歌 製作認真嘅專輯都覺得值得買<br />\n通常都係去女人街 威威 節拍 再行埋去德發地牢<br />\n好多時都平過HMV"},{"pid":"d54f7dd0722b2e7d6d4a9d7292b81a36730d217c","tid":624763,"uid":89866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T02:42:21.000Z","msg":"想搵2手 尋下寶嘅<br />\n通常咪信和10樓撞下<br />\n2手黎講 佢價錢都算合理"},{"pid":"ef56411dd833135a81d2b25012b751e419a02c12","tid":624763,"uid":79120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T02:53:09.000Z","msg":"巴打又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日本band就amazon jp / hmv jp<br />\n有時會去yesasia格下價<br />\n<br />\n二手碟就信和10樓/淘寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1389b9ba8a162066647109a7d4d62f3077e0206","tid":624763,"uid":63150,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T02:56:29.000Z","msg":"CD 音質低<br />\n比更多既錢買低質野個心硬係不太好受<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nps jpop 買cd <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57dde2e7038a192b9001257d7b6bc86eed7db054","tid":624763,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T02:57:04.000Z","msg":"有買呀<br />\n少咗好多"},{"pid":"41e0439ffea44f91fcd64a1d644c8a8145f978e8","tid":624763,"uid":136431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T03:23:31.000Z","msg":"志在收藏嘅感覺<br />\nStreaming Library Save 落一堆 點都唔夠擁有一隻碟嘅感覺滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"881c5c94be6481871505461ccd28affd69b55077","tid":624763,"uid":136431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5b334e2619bde48af7a7d80a2016620d5434659","tid":624763,"u