odite's Child 三隻碟兩舊水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黑膠會上discogs睇，運費仲可以同賣家傾，試過一次鬼佬話終於遇到知音人買佢某隻二手黑膠，送多左隻黑膠同佢demo碟比我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n門市會去信和十樓青木，唔係特別平，但老闆娘好nice好主動介紹碟比你，檢貨見隻黑膠花左會送左比你，叫你揀過隻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n宜家kickstarter都有唔碟集資，之前就買左一隻遊戲Hotline Miami既bgm黑膠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/005/251/566/6be38dfb7f799d9e76c407c5e16f4628_original.jpg?w=680&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1453809926&amp;auto=format&amp;q=92&amp;s=8cf8c424a15cfa76e9786f34fc868730\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fksr-ugc.imgix.net%2Fassets%2F005%2F251%2F566%2F6be38dfb7f799d9e76c407c5e16f4628_original.jpg%3Fw%3D680%26fit%3Dmax%26v%3D1453809926%26auto%3Dformat%26q%3D92%26s%3D8cf8c424a15cfa76e9786f34fc868730&h=d642e0f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"015b2259005b310348e6990e3455fd865e306a32","tid":624763,"uid":8916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:18:42.000Z","msg":"Wowhd"},{"pid":"65dd153fd6c7dddd29fbb3e0012467c27b7a00c0","tid":624763,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:24:28.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣hmv幾好行，啱啱先行完又擺低咗幾舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 見到有抵買（即係唔係三四首歌整幾個remix版本扮大碟嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）又好聽嘅碟就會支持吓，百幾蚊永久擁有隻碟嘅感覺其實好值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04a54f08158b162e86e78684d19a0de1bdd1432","tid":624763,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:25:12.000Z","msg":"why not"},{"pid":"b639f90d491d16fdf509624b953dc0a932d67ebe","tid":624763,"uid":68367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:30:27.000Z","msg":"以前Amazon,hmv買咗百幾二百隻metal CD. <br />\n因爲窮撚屋企細，拆晒所有膠盒入曬落啲100 in one CD 袋到。<br />\n心諗我係聽音樂唔係睇音樂。我諗返起都痛痛地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"811d79d97e61c757ae7b83c5ea1a7865335bbb45","tid":624763,"uid":4120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:32:29.000Z","msg":"hmv jp"},{"pid":"a653448179621078da5f31501416db8d265f5740","tid":624763,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:33:13.000Z","msg":"CD warehouse <br />\n細鋪"},{"pid":"41574d50f90b9348631ca1da83f71aee5fff0e63","tid":624763,"uid":168784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:34:40.000Z","msg":"一直都有買開變左習慣 <br />\n不過就變到好多都無開放左係到"}]}